          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Four silicon telescopes, placed two and two at",
                "symmetrical angles with regard to the beam axis in a",
                "plane perpendicular to the direction of polarization",
                "vector P, were used simultaneously in the measurements.",
                "Accuracy of the telescope angle position setting was",
                " 0.1 degr. Delta E spectrometers with the thicknesses",
                "of 100-200 mu-m were used at small angles and the",
                "spectrometers with the thicknesses of 50-100 mu-m",
                " (in dependence of the beam energy) were used at the",
                "large ones. The thickness of E spectrometers was 2.5-3",
                "mm."
              ]
            }
          ],
